These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk, 7up
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, pall-mall, havana, swisher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, epic, mystery, crime
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, marigold, aconite
 1. the person who growsballoon-flower is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the havana-smoker##1
 3. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
 8. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the havana-smoker##5
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the left or right of the ritmeester-smoker##3
10. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching mystery movies##5
11. the person who growsaconite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking 7up##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage          | 7up     | water   | hot-chocolate | almond-milk |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | ritmeester    | swisher   | havana    |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery       | crime   | epic   | family     |
| Flower     | balloon-flower       | begonia | aconite  | marigold      |

