4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, davidoff, vegafina, bongani
4 different games are played: poker, chess, monopoly, go
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, indie, d&b, ambient
 1. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is in an odd position##4
 3. the person playing go is the american##1
 4. the bongani-smoker is somewhere to the right of the fan of ambient##5
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 6. the fan of ambient is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the game-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the indian##2
 8. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the fan of indie##5
 9. the person playing chess is the bongani-smoker##1
10. the person playing go is somewhere to the right of the indian##5
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |      4       |
| Nationality      | indian       | american | australian     | malaysian     |
| Cigar   | davidoff      | game       | bongani | vegafina |
| Game           | monopoly       | go    | chess     | poker         |
| Music-Genre     | ambient | d&b     | blues     | indie       |

