The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, daffodil, poppy
 1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
 2. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is singing##3
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
 4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the right of the person who growspoppy##5
 5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is surfing##2
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growszinnia##5
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is in an even position##4
10. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person playing poker##1
11. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Game          | snooker    | scrabble      | chess   | poker |
| Hobby   | skydiving | photography | collecting | singing  |
| Sport   | handball   | surfing         | biathlon  | weightlifting  |
