 5. the person playing domino is somewhere to the left of the person who likes coral##5
 6. the person driving the ship is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 7. the person who likes ebony is between the person driving the ship and the person who likes blue##2
 8. the egyptian is on the far left##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
10. the person who likes blue is somewhere to the right of the person who likes coral##5
11. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
12. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person who likes amber##5
13. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5

