 9. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the farmhouse house##5
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
11. the owner of the rabbit is the modern house##1
12. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2       |         3          |     4      |
| House          | farmhouse         | modern         | gothic-revival             | victorian     |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | filmmaking | board-games | skydiving   |
| Color   | yellow   | aquamarine    | lavender            | red        |
| Pet         | rat      | rabbit      | goat           | chinchilla |

