.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-18::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, airplane, motorbike, roller
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, white, green, purple
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, game, vegafina, oliveros
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, soccer, climbing, badminton
