 2. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 3. the old-henry-smoker is between the person driving the taxi and the oliveros-smoker##2
 4. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 5. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3
 6. the person driving the roller is in an odd position##4
 7. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 8. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the game-smoker##5
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
11. the person who's sport is climbing is somewhere to the right of the person driving the roller##5
12. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1

