 1. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who likes light-blue##1
 3. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 4. the person playing canasta is in an even position##4
 5. the person playing go is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
 7. the person playing poker is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 8. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the person playing canasta##5
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
10. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the right of the person who likes azure##5
11. the owner of the chinchilla is somewhere to the right of the person who likes pink##5
12. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5

